{"type":null,"faqId":32082,"title":"How do I change the system font style and size?","answer":"<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 12pt; MARGIN: 8pt 0in 8pt 85.05pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; punctuation-trim: leading\"><span>Download a third-party application to change the system font.</span></p>\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 12pt; MARGIN: 8pt 0in 8pt 85.05pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; punctuation-trim: leading\"><span>To change the system font size, go to the <b>Settings</b> screen and touch <b>Display</b> &gt; <b>Font size</b>. Choose a font size from the displayed option menu.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p> <span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><img style=\"WIDTH: 112.5pt; HEIGHT: 201.75pt\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150707125050355001.jpg\"></span>  <span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><img style=\"WIDTH: 113.25pt; HEIGHT: 201.75pt\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150707125104991001.jpg\"></span>  <span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><img style=\"WIDTH: 113.25pt; HEIGHT: 201.75pt\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150707125118511001.jpg\"></span> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"PAGE-BREAK-AFTER: avoid; POSITION: relative; LINE-HEIGHT: 12pt; MARGIN: 4pt 0in 2pt 85.05pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: 'Book Antiqua','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; TOP: 3pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; punctuation-trim: leading\"><img style=\"WIDTH: 42.75pt; HEIGHT: 12pt\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150707125133961001.png\"></p>\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 10pt; MARGIN: 2pt 0in 4pt 103.